response.original_title: Thin Lizzy:Live At High Voltage Festival 2011
response.overview: Live release from the reunited rockers, recorded during Thin Lizzy's performance on the main stage of the High Voltage festival which was attended by 15,000 people. Thin Lizzy, complete with their new band line up, performed a sensational, energy filled set in which they treated the audience to all their classic tunes from their hugely influential and successful career which spans over four decades. This live recording captures the electric atmosphere of the festival along with sensational renditions of their timeless, chart topping songs of the '70s such as "The Boys are Back in Town" and "Rosalie."
response.tagline: The Boys Are Back In Town
response.title: Thin Lizzy:Live At High Voltage Festival 2011
